room_title: Escape room "The Norwegian Job" by Escape Challenge in Rochester (MN)
review: We were a group of five older woman and we had never tried anything like this before. We had a blast! Glad we were advised to start with the Norwegian room, it was perfect for us! Can't wait to try more, very friendly and helpful employee's also!!

room_title: Escape room "The Norwegian Job" by Escape Challenge in Rochester (MN)
review: My new fiance and I had a great time at Escape Challenge. Not only did we escape in just under an hour but we also got engaged along the way! Nathan worked with me to put together a surprise proposal during the challenge! Thanks for a great experience. We will be back!

room_title: Escape room "The Norwegian Job" by Escape Challenge in Rochester (MN)
review: Can't wait to come back! This was such a fun and unique group activity. I would recommend this for anyone! Family, friends, co-workers... every person in our group had a great time!
